commits.commit_title:
capi: Introduce blaze_normalize_reason_str() helper function

This change introduces the blaze_normalize_reason_str() helper function
that can be used to retrieve a textual representation of a reason for a
normalization failure.

Signed-off-by: Daniel M眉ller <deso@posteo.net>
